    <a href="#terms-o-p" class="max-w-auto px-3 py-[0.45rem] text-sm font-medium text-black bg-neutral-900 rounded-xl hover:bg-neutral-200/50 bg-transparent border border-neutral-300 hover:border-neutral-300 flex items-center gap-2">O - P</a>
